                   === RIFTS EARTH MUD NEWS ===

Welcome to Rifts Earth MUD.

Current state:
  - Praxis: Fully accessible survivor settlement. Explore from Monument Square.
  - Splynn, Atlantis: Alien markets, the Preserves, and slave pens are open.
  - New Camelot, Europe: Magic-rich lands with the Pendragon Inn and Armory.
  - Chi-Town: Coalition territory. Non-humans face open hostility.
  - Lazlo: Peaceful haven for mages and scholars on the Great Lakes.
  - Shops: Use list, buy, sell, value at any vendor.
  - Falconry: Wilderness Scouts and Tribal Warriors start with a trained hawk.
  - Combat: Full APM, strike, parry, dodge, and damage bonus system active.
  - Magic: Ley Line Walkers, Mystics, and Shifters can cast spells via cast.
  - Psionics: Mind Melters and psi-OCCs can use powers via psi.
  - Rest: Find a bunk at the Survivors' Hostel in Praxis to restore HP/SDC.

Upcoming:
  - More races and expanded OCC skill sets.
  - Coalition encounters and faction reputation consequences.
  - Vehicle and Power Armor systems.
  - More Rifts creature encounters in the wilderness.
  - Player housing and estate system.

Report bugs: wish <message>
Contact staff: tell <wizard name> <message>
See who is online: who

Stay alive out there.

